{"tid":410871,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人都係好憎同班所謂咩親戚食飯？","createTime":"2017-09-23T10:20:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-23T11:47:56.000Z","uid":66957,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c6c4c532c2bab4634caba9bfb992ec1275371ffd","tid":410871,"uid":66957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T10:20:32.000Z","msg":"由細到大同呢班親戚講野既次數都好少<br />\n每次問既都係今年幾歲 讀緊咩科 諗住第時做咩<br />\n今次問完答完 下次見面又係問返同一樣既問題<br />\n同d什麼表哥表姐更加從來都唔會傾計<br />\n因為我同我家姐係最細既 <br />\n同我年齡最接近既表哥都大我8年 <br />\n最大既表姐甚至大我2x年<br />\n更加冇可能傾到計<br />\n每次有d咩鳩節日咩鳩生日都要被逼上去出席食飯<br />\n話唔去老豆又黑晒口面咁 <br />\n班親戚仲要講黎講去既話題都係佢地d仔女點叻點勁 搵幾錢一個月<br />\n仲要成班都係親中既仆街<br />\n係到吹奏大陸狗 真係聽到火都黎 <br />\n又唔可以屌佢地<br />\n每次去食飯真係慘撚過落地獄"},{"pid":"b231784cff265444dc551e1eeb912791b6437d9f","tid":410871,"uid":1627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T10:22:17.000Z","msg":"反而我同表哥表姐既關係幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c60364c37f065d355d47f166c49494fdde3521b4","tid":410871,"uid":64277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T11:11:47.000Z","msg":"就算只係一年見一次都唔想去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0ce9231e34a18e72a1ee728655d16b4e532510d","tid":410871,"uid":60793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T11:13:17.000Z","msg":"覺"},{"pid":"adad64bc300f0c6237b6f8c004ad8bdc33be2942","tid":410871,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T11:15:55.000Z","msg":"一樣，去都又無嘢講，仲要成班親中乃共，攪到好似異類咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔去老母又黑晒面"},{"pid":"c171e3a3472d7ef625cb3268bd34a7af1396c9da","tid":410871,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T11:16:53.000Z","msg":"反正唔洗俾錢"},{"pid":"4f214a0f5005ca6031b17f5ded93f4aa796f2554","tid":410871,"uid":102214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T11:17:57.000Z","msg":"去到係冇嘢講。如果我唔去 班親戚又會俾說話阿爸阿媽聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好撚煩"},{"pid":"7677fd9d7a9c6c590d70c34f169bebdca0d66ae7","tid":410871,"uid":46212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T11:18:13.000Z","msg":"憎<br />\n所有親戚都奶共<br />\n佢地子女就正正常常"},{"pid":"40d4e0945f4b7f3cf040de5f77faa627acefa35b","tid":410871,"uid":119379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T11:47:56.000Z","msg":"有少少啦<br />\n但親戚一場，過時過節一定要返去食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}